com.android.apksig

Class ApkSignerEngine.InputJarEntryInstructions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.apksig.ApkSignerEngine.InputJarEntryInstructions
  • Enclosing interface:
    ApkSignerEngine

    public static class ApkSignerEngine.InputJarEntryInstructions
extends Object
    Instructions about how to handle an input APK's JAR entry.

    The instructions indicate whether to output the entry (see getOutputPolicy()) and may contain a request to inspect the entry (see getInspectJarEntryRequest()), in which case the request must be fulfilled before ApkSignerEngine.outputJarEntries() is invoked.
